  "original_title": "\u0db8\u0dc4\u0db4\u0ddc\u0dc5\u0da7, \u0dc1\u0dd2\u0dc2\u0dca\u200d\u0dba\u0dcf\u0db0\u0dcf\u0dbb\u0dc0\u0dbd\u0da7 \u0d9c\u0dd2\u0dba \u0dc0\u0dc3\u0dbb\u0dda \u0db8\u0dd2\u0dbd\u0dd2\u0dba\u0db1 2000\u0d9a\u0dca \u0dc0\u0dd0\u0dba \u0d9a\u0dbb\u0dbd\u0dcf",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "2000 million was spent on Mahapola and bursaries last year",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Last year, 2000 million rupees were spent as scholarships and bursaries for university students.",
        "Last year, the number of students who received Mahapola scholarship was 62891 and the number of students who received scholarship was 29491.",
        "Mahapola and bursaries will be given under the limit of annual household income of 5 lakh rupees.",
        "For the 2020/2021 academic year, 41,755 students are registered in universities, and under the current situation in the country, those students are studying online."
      ],
